rComments: Joanne is the best teacher in Visual Studies.... She is the only one that co-ordinates life models. She actually cares about her students pursuits beyond the classroom. Do well in her class by presenting your values and interests as a cohesive part of your practice. Lower your guard and speak candidly.

Professor Tod gave us complete freedom, and helped whenever there were problems. Amazing learning experience.
